I am not going to do your work for you... But your question can be summed up as &quot;Why am I getting SQL injection?&quot;

The answer is &quot;Because I am dynamically creating SQL queries&quot;, the solution is: **Stop making dynamically created SQL queries.** Once you stop doing that, all your problems go away.. How do you stop? Use `PreparedStatement()` with variable binding (parameterized queries).

